rows.label: tlk45450112_01_msg0001
rows.name:
A hundred grand...that's quite
the pretty little sum.

rows.label: tlk45450112_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Yeah, I've never been paid anything
like this much before.

rows.label: tlk45450112_01_msg0003
rows.name:
And you get another hundred grand
when you get back? Lucky you. What
I wouldn't give for that kind of money...

rows.label: tlk45450112_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Haha, I'm not trying to guilt you
or anything. You just do your best
out there, all right?
